column2: Earl Warren has used the most powerful tool available to him, the Constitution, to save Russia.
Young Poles, infused with the power of the Internet, roam the countryside, terrorizing the populace and destroying infrastructure.
The Bytecoin, hallmark of the Cyberstate economy, has crashed! We have hard times ahead of us.
Roads, aqueducts, and small Roman cities have sprung up all around this province. It's only a matter of time before the populace begins to embrace Roman culture and assimilate into our nation.
The Krishna Kulture Korps roam our streets, keeping true Aryans safe and terrorizing undesirables.
